CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper May 21, 1960, pg. 20, reads: "Champ at Work - Pennsylvania state middleweight champion Johnny Morris, right, looks like he means business in a tow-round exhibition bout with the North Side's Connie Vaughan at the Centre Avenue YMCA last Saturday night. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Boxers Connie Vaughan and Johnny Morris boxing in ring in Centre Avenue YMCA
